land]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''11'''||[[Kevin Kilbane]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''9'''||[[Niall Quinn]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''10''' ||[[Robbie Keane]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Substitutions:'''\n|-\n|GK ||'''16'''||[[Dean Kiely]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''12'''||[[Gary Kelly (footballer, born 1974)|Gary Kelly]]|| ||{{subon|83}}\n|-\n|DF ||'''13''' ||[[Kenny Cunningham]]|| ||{{subon|75}}\n|-\n|MF ||'''15'''||[[Mark Kinsella]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''17'''||[[Lee Carsley]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''18'''||[[Clinton Morrison]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''14'''||[[David Connolly]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Manager:'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\"|[[Mick McCarthy]]\n|}\n|valign=\"top\" width=\"50%\"|\n{| style=\"font-size: 90%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=center\n|-\n!width=\"25\"| !!width=\"25\"|\n|-\n|GK ||'''12''' ||[[Ebrahim Mirzapour]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''2''' ||[[Mehdi Mahdavikia]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''3''' ||[[Mehrdad Minavand]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''5''' ||[[Afshin Peyrovani]] || || {{yel|19}}\n|-\n|DF ||'''6''' ||[[Karim Bagheri]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''7''' ||[[Hamed Kavianpour]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''8''' ||[[Ali Karimi]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''10''' ||[[Ali Daei]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''11'''||[[Alireza Vahedi Nikbakht]]|| ||{{suboff|45}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''15'''||[[Yahya Golmohammadi]] || || {{yel|86}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''24''' ||[[Rahman Rezaei]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Substitutions:'''\n|-\n|MF ||'''9'''||[[Sirous Dinmohammadi]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''13'''||[[Javad Nekounam]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''14'''||[[Mojahed Khaziravi]] || ||{{subon|45}}\n|-\n|MF ||'''18'''||[[Ali Samereh]] || ||{{subon|71}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''20''' ||[[Behrouz Rahbarifar]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''21'''||[[Faraz Fatemi]]\n|-\n|GK ||'''22'''||[[Davoud Fanaei]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Manager:'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\"|{{flagicon|BIH}} [[Miroslav Bla\u017eevi\u0107]]\n|}\n|}\n{| width=100% style=\"font-size: 90%\"\n| width=50% valign=top|\n'''OFFICIALS'''\n*Assistant referees:\n**[[Jorge Oliveira]] ([[Brazilian Football Confederation|Brazil]])\n**[[Aristeu Tavares]] ([[Brazilian Football Confederation|Brazil]])\n*Fourth official: [[Paulo C\u00e9sar de Oliveira]] ([[Brazilian F